With ubuntu.
In a terminal:
To install mono develop:
sudo apt-get install monodevelop
To install svn:
sudo apt-get install subversion

Checkout sirius code:
 svn checkout https://sema.unfuddle.com/svn/sema_sirius2009/ ~/sema_sirius2009 --username yourUserName

Start monodevelop:
monodevelop
Puis charger le fichier /Code/Sirius.sln
